<h2 id="research-interests">Research Interests</h2>

<ul>
  <li>Combinatorial algebraic geometry and topology, computational algebraic geometry, tropical geometry, combinatorics. One of my favorite things to study is the equvariant (co)homology of combinatorially-defined spaces.</li>
</ul>

