<h2 id="outreach">Outreach</h2>

<h3 id="math-circle">Math Circle</h3>
<p><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Spring 2019 - May 2022</code></p>
<ul>
  <li>We organize weekly trips (virtual meetings) to a local middle school and a local high school to teach math through activities and games.</li>
  <li>We also organize public math circles open to everyone in the community.</li>
</ul>

<h3 id="girlsgetmath--icerm">GirlsGetMath @ ICERM</h3>
<p><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Summer 2019</code></p>
<ul>
  <li>This program is for high school gender minority students. It aims to encourage participants to explore math through interactive lectures and hands-on activities. I worked as a TA for the program and gave a lecture on apportionment.</li>
</ul>

<h3 id="summer-science-program">Summer Science Program</h3>
<p><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Summer 2018</code></p>
<ul>
  <li>This astrophysics program is aimed at advanced high school students. I worked as a TA to assist learning in math, physics, astronomy, and computer science.</li>
</ul>

